[mixpanel_people://<name>]
mixpanel_project = Select project credentials to be used for this input.
enable_kvstore = Write records to specified kvstore.
enable_index = Write records to specified index.
kvstore_fields = JSON formatted object of fields and field types for Mixpanel kvstore fields and lookup definition. If object fails to validate, records will be stored in kvstore but only available via the REST API.

[mixpanel_export://<name>]
mixpanel_project = Select project credentials to be used for this input.
project_tz = Timezone configured for project (see project settings in Mixpanel).

[mixpanel_live://<name>]
mixpanel_project = Select project credentials to be used for this input.